# Only sync the RFID folder to GitHub.
# Everything else in this Obsidian vault stays local.
*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/RFID/
!/RFID/**

# macOS / system files
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon

# Temporary Office files
~$*.docx
~$*.pptx
~$*.xlsx

# Logs / databases / generated data
*.log
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db

# GitHub hard limit / very large reference files
# Keep these locally unless you decide to use Git LFS.
RFID/入门资料1/RFID与传感器网络 (Pdg2Pic, （挪）张彦，（加）杨，陈积明编著) (z-library.sk, 1lib.sk, z-lib.sk).pdf
